A week in my life. I have always taken any tattoo. I do not turn down business. I treat my clients how I’d like to be treated, I’ll do any tattoo in color or black and grey.  If you’re a young tattooer I highly suggest getting good at everything and not sticking with one type of tattoo style. I also suggest taking your photos and not putting a thousand filters on them to make you feel better about how it looks. The internet is not real life and people will come back to you if your tattoos are solid. I appreciate everyone past and present who’s been tattooed by me and I look forward to my future clients. Thank you all
